data.name: label8.Text
data.value:
-Main manu- 1) inmate information text box 2) Camera Conrtol Panel 3) start new mugshot process 4) Calibrate Camera 5) Take front mugshot 6) Take side mugshot 7) Save mugshots 8) Open the Application Settings Menu 9) Open the Help Menu
-application settings menu- 10) change the file path to save mugshots. 11) select the camera you want to use 12) if you have PTZ camera, select corresponding controller. if not, select "no contoller" 13) change if you want to open the folder when saved mugshot 14) change if you want to override mugshots each time or keep every mugshots taken. 15) change the naming convention for the mugshot's file names 16) change if you want to create combined image 17) save settings changed.
